<td>1:4 and up</td>
<td>254&#160;mm and up
</td>
<td><span class="nowrap">10&#160;in</span> (<span class="nowrap">254&#160;mm</span>). Several large scales exist, but are not strictly model railroading gauges. Instead, they are used mostly in commercial settings, such as <a href="/wiki/Amusement_park" title="Amusement park">amusement park</a> <a href="/wiki/Amusement_ride" class="mw-redirect" title="Amusement ride">rides</a>.</td>
